announcement that it would use corporate cash to buy the asset and accept i=
t as a form of payment for its vehicles. Ethereum, the second-biggest coin,=
 sank more than 40%, while joke token Dogecoin lost 45%. ...</p><p style=3D=
"margin: 16px 0;">Tesla CEO Elon Musk sparked the wild moves last week. Bit=
