er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;"> I wrote</a>, ugh, Monday that Musk has the a=
bility to make Bitcoin go up or down whenever he wants, with his tweets, wi=
